      <label><span>Lookback period</span><div class="unit-field"><input name="lookbackYears" type="number" min="0" max="10" step="0.25" value="3" required /><b>yr</b></div></label>
    </div>
    <div class="form-error" data-exposure-error role="alert" hidden></div>
    <div class="tool-actions"><button class="button" type="submit">Calculate snapshot <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></button><button class="reset-button" type="reset">Reset example</button></div>
    <p class="privacy-note">No inputs are sent anywhere. This page has no analytics or tracking script.</p>
  </form>
  <section class="exposure-result" data-exposure-results tabindex="-1" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="tool-panel-head"><p class="data-label">Wages-only result</p><span>Not a claim valuation</span></div>
    <p class="result-prefix">At the inputs shown</p>
    <strong class="result-amount" data-exposure-amount>$131,040</strong>
    <p class="result-label">illustrative straight-time wages</p>
    <div class="formula-strip"><span data-formula-count>12 employees</span><b>×</b><span data-formula-gap>2.5 hr/week</span><b>×</b><span data-formula-rate>$28.00/hr</span><b>×</b><span data-formula-weeks>156 weeks</span></div>
    <div class="result-grid">
      <div><h2>What this includes</h2><p>Only the entered group size, estimated weekly time gap, average regular rate, and lookback period.</p></div>
      <div><h2>What this excludes</h2><ul data-exclusions></ul></div>
    </div>
    <aside><strong>Read the number narrowly.</strong><p>A real matter can involve different rates, time periods, employees, legal theories, defenses, and records. This model does not resolve any of them.</p></aside>
    <button class="print-button no-print" type="button" data-print-exposure>Print snapshot</button>
  </section>
</div>

